14 journeyman plumber shall be employed and supervised by a licensed
15 plumbing contractor.
16 5. A residential journeyman shall not contract or furnish labor
17 and materials.
18 6. A residential journeyman performs plumbing work as an
19 apprentice in commercial industrial plumbing under a licensed
20 plumbing contractor and an apprentice registration with the State of
21 Oklahoma.
22 7. Applicants for a journeyman plumber examination shall be
23 eighteen (18) years of age or older and have:
24
